 2023-10462023-10-20JUS
ActOther Than Statutory Authority
PrecisAppointment of the HONOURABLE ALICE WOOLLEY, a Justice of the Court of King's Bench of Alberta, to be a Justice of Appeal of the Court of Appeal of Alberta, and a Judge ex officio of the Court of King's Bench of Alberta; and to be a Judge of the Court of Appeal of the Northwest Territories and a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Nunavut during her tenure of office as a Justice of Appeal of the Court of Appeal of Alberta.
